rships and Awards CoB General and Departmental Scholarships Scholarship descriptions, requirements and online application UNT Scholarships Student Financial Aid & Scholarships Office for Nationally Competitive Scholarship Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA) Exam Scholarships The FIREL faculty can sponsor students for the upcoming Chartered Financial Analyst exam. The CFA program provides an important certification for those working or intending to work in the investments profession. The scholarship will reduce the CFA Program enrollment and exam registration fee (includes access to the curriculum eBook) to US$350. This is a potential value of $1,000 or more. Scholarships Sources Outside UNT Absolutely Scholarships FastWeb Rose Crawford Memorial Scholarship Rose Crawford Memorial Scholarship sponsored by the Greater Denton Wise County Association of REALTORS@ (GDWCAR) for students pursuing an education in the real estate industry. Completed application materials should be submitted directly to GDWCAR office by January 31. Contact GDWCAR with any questions or for additional information: http://www.gdwcar.com/ or 940/387-8212. Scholarships.com SOCIETY OF INDUSTRIAL AND OFFICE REALTORS® (SIOR)MATCHING SCHOLARSHIP FUND APPLICATION Application deadline: March 1, 2017 Application Physical Address: University of North Texas College of Business 1307 West Highland Street Denton, Texas 76201 Contact the College of Business Mailing Address: University of North Texas College of Business 1155 Union Circle #311160 Denton, TX 76203-5017 Contact the College of Business This Website: © 2017 UNT College of Business For issues or comments related to this website, please contact us.   Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Web Accessibility | State of Texas Online | Emergency Preparedness | THECB Online Resume System 